</div>

<div type="history" n="locations">
<head>Locations</head>
<p>Found: <rs type="found">in what may be an altar foundation in the <rs type="monuList">North Agora</rs>, along with coins covering a long period from Hellenistic onwards, as well as animal bones.</rs> Original location: <rs type="origLocation">Unknown</rs>. Last recorded: <rs type="lastLocation">Museum (1988)</rs>.</p>
</div>





